如果你的目的只是：

驗證 VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 和 BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT 的 CustomerNo + IsSARFiled 是否完全一致

那根本不用繞一大圈。

找出有差異的資料

SELECT
    v.CustomerNo,
    v.IsSARFiled AS VERIFY_IsSARFiled,
    b.IsSARFiled AS BSA_IsSARFiled
FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
FULL OUTER JOIN BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT b
    ON v.CustomerNo = b.CustomerNo
WHERE ISNULL(CAST(v.IsSARFiled AS INT),-1)
    <> ISNULL(CAST(b.IsSARFiled AS INT),-1);

如果結果：

0 rows

代表全部一致 ✅

⸻

或用 EXCEPT 驗證

VERIFY 有但 BSA 不同：

SELECT CustomerNo,
       CAST(IsSARFiled AS INT) AS IsSARFiled
FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
EXCEPT
SELECT CustomerNo,
       CAST(IsSARFiled AS INT) AS IsSARFiled
FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT;

BSA 有但 VERIFY 不同：

SELECT CustomerNo,
       CAST(IsSARFiled AS INT) AS IsSARFiled
FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
EXCEPT
SELECT CustomerNo,
       CAST(IsSARFiled AS INT) AS IsSARFiled
FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT;

如果兩支都回傳：

0 rows

那就代表：

CustomerNo
IsSARFiled

兩個欄位的資料 100% 一致。

